  [Text] Recently, the Northwest Petroleum Geology Bureau of 
the Ministry of Geology and Mineral Resources verified a 
medium-sized oil and gas field with impressive geological 
reserves. The field is located in the northern part of the Tarim 
Basin in Luntai Xian, Xinjiang Province. 
  The field has been named the "Western Daliya" oil and gas 
field and it covers an area of 11.5 square kilometers. The 
deposit has a thickness of 17.4 meters. 

