</HEADER>

<ABS>  China </ABS>
<DATE1>   22 October 1993 </DATE1>
<F P=100> Energy </F>
<F P=101> Nuclear Power </F>
<H3> <TI>   Research Lab of High-Flux Engineering Test Reactor </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Research Lab of High-Flux Engineering Test Reactor </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   946B0024A Chengdu SICHUAN RIBAO in Chinese 22 Oct 93 p 3 </F>
<F P=103> 946B0024A </F>
<F P=104>  Chengdu SICHUAN RIBAO </F>
<F P=105>  Chinese </F>


